
<p>What a great site (<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/nflplayoffscenarios.com">and Bluesky account</a>) this is. Just what it says on the tin: all the scenarios for how the NFL playoff seedings can shake out, presented very plainly but clearly. The old-school World Wide Web still has a beating heart.</p>

